{"tid":2266450,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"2020年Q3，台灣經濟成長率3.33%，穩居亞洲四小龍第一，新加坡負7%","createTime":"2020-11-01T10:22:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-02T11:28:33.000Z","uid":109923,"like":72,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"ca4ab29d01d069a6f4faf3a60289ea38610e4fad","tid":2266450,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T10:22:36.000Z","msg":"台灣經濟的好表現，再次超越了預測！<br />\n　　<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O4u97W8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO4u97W8.jpg&h=a0a90e2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最近各國陸續公布2020年第三季 #經濟成長率，其中台灣的經濟成長率來到3.33%，比預期更好，也穩居亞洲四小龍第一名。<br />\n　　<br />\n經濟能維持正成長，要歸功於國人團結防疫、社會上百工百業認真打拚，這是我們共同的成績！<br />\n　　<br />\n好成績就該延續下去，疫情過後，台灣也不能忽視和其他國家的經貿往來。包括加速進行各重大投資計畫、推動產業轉型，以及布局跨國的供應鏈合作網路，都是我正在帶領政府團隊努力的方向。<br />\n　　<br />\n假日午後，請大家幫我把好成績、好消息，分享給身邊的親朋好友知道吧！"},{"pid":"96ec5397e8336569f5592e545df0d13b2a6f84fb","tid":2266450,"uid":109923,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T15:31:59.000Z","msg":"新加坡做乜咁慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6adf4b5cfec457f9801530d392d654b6b13f7d7e","tid":2266450,"uid":9710,"like":25,"dislike":3,"score":22,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T15:42:25.000Z","msg":"但其實四小龍其餘三隻都已經拋離左台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95af2c712d04a2e6acd98d351bc0ed2ff677cfcd","tid":2266450,"uid":3369,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T15:46:22.000Z","msg":"應該全亞洲除咗越南同台灣都冇第個國家可以有增長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8004302fa73b12a2302d6d35a2c7b7acb8966d26","tid":2266450,"uid":66087,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6adf4b5cfec457f9801530d392d654b6b13f7d7e","tid":2266450,"uid":9710,"like":25,"dislike":3,"score":22,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T15:42:25.000Z","msg":"但其實四小龍其餘三隻都已經拋離左台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/